annotations.title: Master The Classics: Daiquiri

textContent:
2oz or 60ml Rum
1oz or 30ml Lime Juice
.75oz or 20ml Simple Syrup (Rich Cane Syrup if available)
Lime Wheel Garnish

Shake and double strain into coupe
Garnish with lime wheel
